{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Brand story page",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "story-page-section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "header", "content": "Hero" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "hero_image", "label": "Hero image (desktop)" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "hero_image_mobile", "label": "Hero image (mobile)" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_title", "label": "Hero title", "default": "Ventral. Level the Sea." },
    { "type": "header", "content": "Who we are" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro_heading", "label": "Heading", "default": "WHO WE ARE" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "intro_text",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>You go to the water for clarity. To focus. To disconnect. But water never stays still. Wind shifts. Currents move. Your position drifts. And when your craft feels unsteady, so do you. Ventral changes that.</p><p>We design every vessel for greater control on the water. Intelligent systems help you manage your position in wind and current. Precision handling helps you stay where you want when the water won't. It responds instantly to your input—so every adjustment feels natural. When the platform feels steady, your focus returns to the mission, not the motion.</p><p>We build for confidence on the water. To fish spots others skip. To explore places most never reach. Stand steady. Move freely. Go farther.</p><p>Ventral. Level the Sea.</p>"
    },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "who_background", "label": "Background image (desktop)" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "who_background_mobile", "label": "Background image (mobile)" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "who_image", "label": "Scene image (desktop)" },
    { "type": "image_picker", "id": "who_image_mobile", "label": "Scene image (mobile)" },
    { "type": "header", "content": "Anchor with ease" },
